precis:
Enactment of the OVERPAYMENTS TO CERTAIN MEMBERS OF THE CANADIAN FORCES
REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of overpayments made
between December 1, 1977 and December 31, 1994, to members and former
members (or their dependents) who were reclassified as pilots.
